{"tid":1345284,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完BBC 既報導，有啲嬲","createTime":"2019-07-22T01:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T03:50:57.000Z","uid":89462,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c5b5da251519958d20871ebb037f127c37653687","tid":1345284,"uid":89462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:45:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49066982\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49066982&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqVNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=abbbe7df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49066982&h=e552268f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49066982</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The mob stormed Yuen Long MTR station at about 22:30 local time (14:30 GMT), hours after clashes betrween protestors and police in the Sheung Wan area earlier in the day.</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">將金鐘同元朗放埋一齊講，明顯會令人覺得呢班人係同一夥</span><br />\n<br />\nYuen Long is a more remote district of Hong Kong, and is far away from the site of the main pro-democracy protests.<br />\n<br />\nWhat happened at the rally earlier on Sunday?<br />\nRiot police fired tear gas and rubber bullets at protesters in Hong Kong at a large pro-democracy rally, and charged demonstrators who threw objects at police lines.<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"> 明顯BBC 係咩都唔知，淨係睇左政府張公告，然後將兩單嘢放埋一齊講</span><br />\n<br />\nThe protest route was altered with protesters told to stop at Wan Chai rather than Central, where the key government offices are located.<br />\n<br />\nSome 4,000 police officers were deployed.<br />\n<br />\nBonnie Leung from the Civil Human Rights Front urged Hong Kong leader Carrie Lam to &quot;stop turning a deaf ear to the Hong Kong people's demands&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nOrganisers of Sunday's protest say more than 430,000 people took part but police put the figure at 138,000.<br />\n<br />\nBBC 咩都唔知就唔好求其寫啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e257c098759daa13b3e761de7c9100790d5a34","tid":1345284,"uid":7426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:47:06.000Z","msg":"小弟英文唔好，希望幫你推下，用文宣同外國講"},{"pid":"f33bff1513fd81007a95fb5531d9bfcd2a816975","tid":1345284,"uid":122988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:47:46.000Z","msg":"Triad gangster attack in Hong Kong after night of violent protests-lawmaker<br />\nby Reuters<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.trust.org//item/20190722011033-76kfs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.trust.org%2F%2Fitem%2F20190722011033-76kfs%2F&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqVNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=afc08bf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.trust.org//item/20190722011033-76kfs/</a><br />\n<br />\nSky news : Masked attackers beat Hong Kong protesters in subway<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sky.com/video/attackers-beat-hong-kong-protesters-in-subway-11768042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fvideo%2Fattackers-beat-hong-kong-protesters-in-subway-11768042&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqVNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=00f8df5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sky.com/video/attackers-beat-hong-kong-protesters-in-subway-11768042</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nindependent: Armed mob attacks commuters as police fire rubber bullets at demonstrators as democracy march descends into chaos<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/hong-kong-protests-china-tear-gas-graffiti-march-eggs-liaison-office-a9014566.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-china-tear-gas-graffiti-march-eggs-liaison-office-a9014566.html&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqVNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=fc802b1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/hong-kong-protests-china-tear-gas-graffiti-march-eggs-liaison-office-a9014566.html</a><br />\n<br />\nBloomberg: Tear Gas, Attacks and Warnings<br />\n Fuel Hong Kong Anxiety<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-07-21/thousands-set-to-turn-out-for-anti-government-march-in-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-07-21%2Fthousands-set-to-turn-out-for-anti-government-march-in-hong-kong&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqVNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=c7410c04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-07-21/thousands-set-to-turn-out-for-anti-government-march-in-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"32c0667d3b1c392c0e24810943acfbe970e55133","tid":1345284,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:47:59.000Z","msg":"你睇埋下面佢quote兩段twitter片 就知個立場"},{"pid":"d15c450bf1ae4ded02608ce9978e99b3b5642ad8","tid":1345284,"uid":109629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:48:17.000Z","msg":"文宣組做野<br />\n<br />\n直接俾料佢地"},{"pid":"08852157a0fb9b5a22e646ab7bf88f0f409048fe","tid":1345284,"uid":39239,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:49:00.000Z","msg":"唔好唔記得幾年前本土派成日俾西霉抹黑，佢哋呢班係海外死左膠"},{"pid":"fa1219abb1cfb94c08b9907d2eecf96d04a0f8d6","tid":1345284,"uid":211958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:49:00.000Z","msg":"求元朗時序線<br />\n雖然英文唔好，但我想試下打做英文俾大家share"},{"pid":"8e3de5640f33107a17de1224dab7eedd518dd595","tid":1345284,"uid":90183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:52:03.000Z","msg":"求英文好幫幫手<br />\n政府想令外國以為白衫黑社會人士係示威者"},{"pid":"1817ab4de2cf863c529b5e53438e3cefce7943fd","tid":1345284,"uid":243380,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:53:00.000Z","msg":"Understandable.. they do not have reliable intel in English. That is why we need to let them know what really is happening. The HK government is not trustworthy."},{"pid":"3ac75d0d55da7ba0d0c8f996e90b3f1ded80f693","tid":1345284,"uid":147010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:06:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"39cec2ac0e6d4b6a2d8d86cc2a73319933de9b7f","tid":1345284,"uid":50901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:09:21.000Z","msg":"以正視聽<br />\n英文好的巴絲快幫手翻譯多d資料"},{"pid":"d81fd3d2142e5009deab8858641d3bf0872b18c2","tid":1345284,"uid":89462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:27:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你睇埋下面佢quote兩段twitter片 就知個立場</blockquote><br />\nThe mob attack followed the latest pro-democracy rally in the centre of Hong Kong, where riot police had fired tear gas and rubber bullets at protesters.<br />\n呢段話暴徒既襲擊係接續住反送中遊行，時間點係係防暴隊釋放催淚彈及發射橡膠子彈之後。<br />\n<br />\nIt is unclear who the mob were, but they attacked passengers and people making their way back from the protest.<br />\nBBC 話並唔清楚呢班暴徒係咩人，但係佢地襲擊乘客，以及參加完示威既群眾。<br />\n<br />\n然後BBC 就報導返政府果張公告。明顯唔知元朗發生咩事。但放左係同一單新聞入邊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"183602c784a3317829d98b29186d09ca7a207a75","tid":1345284,"uid":87295,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:39:31.000Z","msg":"just now i sent a message to the reporter at bloomberg (natalie lung), hope she will see my message and be in contact soon."},{"pid":"eb90d8c2b0c7701b469551b1895e19b805073641","tid":1345284,"uid":87295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:42:17.000Z","msg":"大家幫手搵下bbc contact, email linked in 乜都得"},{"pid":"0c9731ea1ed597a6ca4705388a89560be22cfb6e","tid":1345284,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:29:42.000Z","msg":"要推比國際知"},{"pid":"3688ac2e81de12a2dc1676ccebdfa1b14635e948","tid":1345284,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:30:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"p